        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1838386422" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3833858113373554646">There was in fact a moment when I was going crazy!!! <br/>First, I applaud the writer -what a brain!-, so smart and knowledgeable!! I also applaud the nurses and staff that work in these centers. It requires a great sacrifice and love for human kind to perform these tasks. <br/>I did like Alice Gould, her wit and her answers to any problem. I also love books where I learn about topics new to me. Very entertaining, and hard to put away. Great book!! </span>

          </span>
