    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer787484641" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9499122960500983041">The author had the opportunity to exploit the story, but he failed. It was a normal novel, slow.. At least half of the book is not relevant for the story and that makes it sometimes a little boring. Some chapters are interesting, you can immerse within. He has an exceptional (and still sometimes boring) capacity to describe. The main character has a charming personality. I had great expectations about this book because of the reviews I had read, but the novel didn&apos;t reach them.</span>
  <span id="freeText9499122960500983041" style="display:none">The author had the opportunity to exploit the story, but he failed. It was a normal novel, slow.. At least half of the book is not relevant for the story and that makes it sometimes a little boring. Some chapters are interesting, you can immerse within. He has an exceptional (and still sometimes boring) capacity to describe. The main character has a charming personality. I had great expectations about this book because of the reviews I had read, but the novel didn't reach them.</span>
