              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer664870015055340337">Touching, amusing, lovely, thrilling and thought-provoking story. The author immerses us in a supposedly marginalized, hopeless and disaffected world: a mental hospital. The readers will experience a bittersweet feeling when facing the surprise of sanity and dementia just being separated by a very thin and blurred line.<br/>A book to be recommended!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


